title: İzmir Demirspor
text:
Izmir Demirspor is a Turkish <a href="Soccer">football</a> club from <a href="Izmir">Izmir</a>. The team was founded in 1955 and plays in blue kits.
Currently the club plays in the <a href="Amat%C3%B6r%20Futbol%20Ligleri">Amatör Futbol Ligleri</a>.
Stadium.
Currently the team plays at the 15500 capacity <a href="%C4%B0zmir%20Alsancak%20Stadium">İzmir Alsancak Stadium</a>.
